45:38.575 --> 45:41.100
Hales, let's go. We don't wanna be late.

45:41.277 --> 45:43.108
I'm coming. I'm coming. I'm sorry.

45:43.279 --> 45:46.806
- I'm nervous. Why am I nervous?
- You're always nervous.

45:46.983 --> 45:48.007
Oh, thank you.

46:02.198 --> 46:03.859
- Caw.
- Ha-ha-ha.

46:04.033 --> 46:06.058
Nobody says "caw," Julian.

46:06.236 --> 46:08.397
We do. We say "caw"
every week on the show.

46:08.571 --> 46:11.972
- Oh, all right, all
right. Caw. - Ha-ha-ha.

46:12.141 --> 46:13.665
- We'll see you there.
- Okay.

47:23.479 --> 47:26.004
It's the oldest story in the world.

47:26.282 --> 47:29.740
One day you're 17 and
planning for someday.

47:32.255 --> 47:35.816
And then, quietly, and without
you ever really noticing...

47:35.992 --> 47:37.289
someday is today.

47:38.661 --> 47:41.061
Then someday is yesterday.

47:43.166 --> 47:45.100
And this is your life.

47:49.138 --> 47:55.202
We spend so much time
wanting, pursuing, wishing.

47:55.912 --> 47:58.073
But ambition is good.

47:58.247 --> 48:01.978
Chasing things with integrity is good.

48:02.251 --> 48:04.082
Dreaming.

48:05.855 --> 48:08.517
If you had a friend you
knew you'd never see again...

48:08.691 --> 48:10.682
what would you say?

48:11.294 --> 48:14.422
If you could do one last
thing for someone you love...

48:14.597 --> 48:16.531
what would it be?

48:17.200 --> 48:18.633
Say it.

48:18.801 --> 48:20.166
Do it.

48:20.336 --> 48:21.963
Don't wait.

48:22.138 --> 48:24.265
Nothing lasts forever.

48:25.174 --> 48:28.041
Make a wish and place it in your heart.

48:30.046 --> 48:32.014
Anything you want.

48:32.315 --> 48:34.476
Everything you want.

48:36.319 --> 48:39.049
Do you have it? Good.

